"assert|verify"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"en"
:
"Verify file hash against expected value (auto-detect algorithm from length). Shows match/mismatch via log output. Returns 0 if match, 1 if mismatch. \"verify\" is an alias for \"assert\"."
,
"cn"
:
"验证文件哈希与预期值（从长度自动检测算法）。通过日志输出显示匹配/不匹配。匹配返回 0，不匹配返回 1。\"verify\" 是 \"assert\" 的别名。"
}
,
"#1"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"en"
:
"file path"
,
"cn"
:
"文件路径"
}
,
"#exec"
:
"___x_cmd_advise__file"
}
,
"#2"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"en"
:
"Expected hash value (32/64/128 chars for MD5/SHA256/SHA512)"
,
"cn"
:
"预期的哈希值（32/64/128 字符对应 MD5/SHA256/SHA512）"
}
}
}
,
"match"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"en"
:
"Match file hash against expected value silently (for scripts). Returns 0 if match, 1 if mismatch, 2 if algorithm unknown. No output."
,
"cn"
:
"静默匹配文件哈希与预期值（用于脚本）。匹配返回 0，不匹配返回 1，无法识别算法返回 2。无输出。"
}
,
"#1"
:
{
"#desc"
:
{
"en"
:
"file path"
,
"cn"
:
"文件路径"
}
,
"#exec"
:
"___x_cmd_advise__file"
}
,
